prompt_text:
Today is 2026-04-21.

Current closing price of FedEx (FDX): $394.59 USD as of 2026-04-21.

Predict the closing price of FedEx at three future horizons. For each horizon, provide a point estimate and a 90% confidence interval. A 90% confidence interval means you are providing a low value and a high value such that you believe there is a 90% chance the true closing price will fall between them. If we asked you to make this kind of estimate 100 times, the true value should fall inside your interval on about 90 of those occasions. Choose your bounds accordingly.

Horizons:
  1-day  target date: 2026-04-22
  1-week target date: 2026-04-28
  1-month target date: 2026-05-21

Respond ONLY with valid JSON and no markdown fences:
{
  "1d": {
    "point_estimate": <number>,
    "90_ci": [<low>, <high>]
  },
  "1w": {
    "point_estimate": <number>,
    "90_ci": [<low>, <high>]
  },
  "1m": {
    "point_estimate": <number>,
    "90_ci": [<low>, <high>]
  }
}

